I"ƒ<h1 id="pc-engines-apu-coreboot-open-source-firmware-v41204">PC Engines apu coreboot Open Source Firmware v4.12.0.4</h1>

<h2 id="key-changes">Key changes</h2>

<p>Mainline:</p>

<ol>
  <li><strong>Rebased</strong> with official coreboot repository <strong>commit</strong> 81a2f45.</li>
  <li><strong>Fixed</strong> TPM2 visibility in OS for apu3d and apu4d.</li>
  <li><strong>Fixed</strong> issues with IRQ vectors reported in Xen and Linux dmesg.</li>
  <li><strong>Updated sortbootorder</strong> to version <strong>v4.6.20</strong> adding minor build fix for
mainline coreboot.</li>
</ol>

