<h3 id="key-changes-in-testing">Key Changes in testing</h3>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>PC Engines apu1d has been integrated into Automated Regression
infrastructure. This immediately greatly increased the range of tests.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>There were some hardware modifications, apu3d and apu4d has been added TPM2.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Some USB sticks has been replaced - this decreased the number some random
issues.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Xen is still unstable - this is the cause of over a half of the failures.</p>
  </li>
</ol>

